00:04:36.420 --> 00:04:38.840 align:middle line:84%
So if our universe
is a great thought

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:41.780 align:middle line:84%
in the mind of the
cosmos, then our universe

00:04:41.780 --> 00:04:44.880 align:middle line:84%
