cosmos itself is pure mind.

00:07:26.510 --> 00:07:27.740 align:middle line:90%
Pure mind.

00:07:27.740 --> 00:07:31.640 align:middle line:84%
And what we talk of as matter
actually seems very solid,

00:07:31.640 --> 00:07:32.760 align:middle line:90%
