00:07:32.760 --> 00:07:35.750 align:middle line:84%
It's very ephemeral
and foundationally it's

00:07:35.750 --> 00:07:38.070 align:middle line:90%
mind and consciousness.

00:07:38.070 --> 00:07:40.520 align:middle line:84%
