00:49:34.670 --> 00:49:36.720 align:middle line:84%
whether we're
aware of it or not.

00:49:36.720 --> 00:49:40.160 align:middle line:84%
And our conscious
mind, our aware mind

00:49:40.160 --> 00:49:45.980 align:middle line:84%
processes a tiny, tiny, tiny
proportion of the information

00:49:45.980 --> 00:49:48.330 align:middle line:90%
that's always available to us.

00:49:48.330 --> 00:49:50.640 align:middle line:84%
But when we're willing
to open ourselves--

00:49:50.640 --> 00:49:53.420 align:middle line:84%
and it is literally
as simple as that,

00:49:53.420 --> 00:49:55.700 align:middle line:84%
although there are various
modalities that have been

00:49:55.700 --> 00:50:00.150 align:middle line:84%
