And yet there is a
fundamental commonality.

00:51:12.580 --> 00:51:16.010 align:middle line:84%
We're all human in
a human community.

00:51:16.010 --> 00:51:22.510 align:middle line:84%
So we're all co-creators of
our collective human psyche.

00:51:22.510 --> 00:51:28.640 align:middle line:84%
We're all different notes in
this amazing cosmic symphony.

