We're all players in
an improv jazz session

00:51:33.130 --> 00:51:34.630 align:middle line:84%
because we don't
know what's coming.

00:51:34.630 --> 00:51:37.640 align:middle line:84%
So that symphony
is not yet written.

00:51:37.640 --> 00:51:40.970 align:middle line:84%
We're all showing up to
be improv jazz players.

00:51:40.970 --> 00:51:46.130 align:middle line:84%
And improv jazz players, they
