with this remembering

00:52:27.500 --> 00:52:32.990 align:middle line:84%
and cleaning up to help sort out
our inner traumas and patterns

00:52:32.990 --> 00:52:34.790 align:middle line:90%
that no longer serve us.

00:52:34.790 --> 00:52:38.240 align:middle line:84%
Then we can show up,
not from our ego,

00:52:38.240 --> 00:52:42.170 align:middle line:84%
but we can show up in
service as a world server,

00:52:42.170 --> 00:52:45.380 align:middle line:84%
in service to something
that's greater than we are.

00:52:45.380 --> 00:52:48.170 align:middle line:90%
And then we can link up.

00:52:48.170 --> 00:52:50.120 align:middle line:90%
And then we can lift up.

00:52:50.120 --> 00:52:51.950 align:middle line:90%
And I feel that's happening.

00:52:51.950 --> 00:52:57.560 align:middle line:84%
And, for me, this is a
process of metamorphosis.

00:52:57.560 --> 00:53:01.970 align:middle line:84%
Metamorphosis is all
about a biological being

00:53:01.970 --> 00:53:04.820 align:middle line:84%
such as a caterpillar
that has the potential

00:53:04.820 --> 00:53:06.650 align:middle line:90%
to become a butterfly.

00:53:06.650 --> 00:53:10.130 align:middle line:84%
And that caterpillar's
job is to eat.

00:53:10.130 --> 00:53:12.470 align:middle line:84%
That caterpillar's
job is to go out

00:53:12.470 --> 00:53:16.650 align:middle line:84%
there and eat as much as it can
regardless of the environment.

00:53:16.650 --> 00:53:19.670 align:middle line:84%
So unless the environment's
in an ecosystem where there

00:53:19.670 --> 00:53:21.740 align:middle line:84%
are enough birds to
eat the caterpillars,

00:53:21.740 --> 00:53:23.280 align:middle line:90%
the caterpillar goes wild.

00:53:23.280 --> 00:53:26.720 align:middle line:84%
But in a healthy ecosystem,
there are enough caterpillars

00:53:26.720 --> 00:53:30.200 align:middle line:84%
and enough birds to ensure that
the caterpillars go forward,

00:53:30.200 --> 00:53:32.510 align:middle line:90%
but they don't eat everything.

00:53:32.510 --> 00:53:34.670 align:middle line:90%
We're like the caterpillar.

00:53:34.670 --> 00:53:37.070 align:middle line:84%
With our fragmented
understanding

00:53:37.070 --> 00:53:38.720 align:middle line:84%
of the nature of
reality, we've eaten

00:53:38.720 --> 00:53:40.390 align:middle line:90%
as much as we possibly can.

00:53:40.390 --> 00:53:43.450 align:middle line:84%
And because we are the dominant
species on this planet,

00:53:43.450 --> 00:53:45.980 align:middle line:84%
we have been able to
eat our environment.

00:53:45.980 --> 00:53:48.730 align:middle line:84%
We've been able to
eat our fellow animals

00:53:48.730 --> 00:53:51.970 align:middle line:84%
and other children of
Gaia because that's

00:53:51.970 --> 00:53:57.340 align:middle line:84%
what our beingness, that's what
our awareness has taken us to.

00:53:57.340 --> 00:54:00.160 align:middle line:84%
But I think now
we're starting to go

00:54:00.160 --> 00:54:04.000 align:middle line:84%
into the chrysalis
of metamorphosis

00:54:04.000 --> 00:54:05.980 align:middle line:90%
because it's not sustainable.

00:54:05.980 --> 00:54:08.350 align:middle line:84%
The way we are, there's
nothing more to eat.

00:54:08.350 --> 00:54:10.910 align:middle line:84%
We've eaten as much
as we possibly can.

00:54:10.910 --> 00:54:13.100 align:middle line:84%
And when a caterpillar
gets to that point,

00:54:13.100 --> 00:54:15.550 align:middle line:84%
it naturally goes
into a chrysalis.

00:54:15.550 --> 00:54:17.140 align:middle line:84%
And when it goes
into a chrysalis,

00:54:17.140 --> 00:54:19.000 align:middle line:90%
it starts to break down.

00:54:19.000 --> 00:54:21.160 align:middle line:90%
Its body breaks down.

00:54:21.160 --> 00:54:24.950 align:middle line:84%
It literally-- its immune
system starts to fail.

00:54:24.950 --> 00:54:26.830 align:middle line:84%
But what happens
within that chrysalis

00:54:26.830 --> 00:54:29.110 align:middle line:90%
is something extraordinary.

00:54:29.110 --> 00:54:32.050 align:middle line:84%
The potential of the
butterfly starts to form,

00:54:32.050 --> 00:54:35.980 align:middle line:84%
and it begins to form in
what's called imaginal cells.

00:54:35.980 --> 00:54:38.320 align:middle line:84%
The beginning of an antenna,
the beginning of an eye,

00:54:38.320 --> 00:54:39.760 align:middle line:90%
the beginning of a wing.

00:54:39.760 --> 00:54:45.470 align:middle line:84%
And as that butterfly starts
to create itself into being,

00:54:45.470 --> 00:54:49.480 align:middle line:84%
the dying caterpillar
attacks it.

00:54:49.480 --> 00:54:52.000 align:middle line:84%
And that attack
strengthens the butterfly.

00:54:52.000 --> 00:54:54.520 align:middle line:84%
The butterfly needs
that dying caterpillar

00:54:54.520 --> 00:54:56.740 align:middle line:90%
to attack it to strengthen it.

00:54:56.740 --> 00:55:00.460 align:middle line:84%
And inevitably, the
caterpillar dissolves away,

00:55:00.460 --> 00:55:02.620 align:middle line:90%
and the butterfly strengthens.

00:55:02.620 --> 00:55:07.600 align:middle line:84%
And then a day comes when that
butterfly is ready to fly.

00:55:07.600 --> 00:55:13.760 align:middle line:84%
And the chrysalis opens,
and the butterfly is free.

00:55:13.760 --> 00:55:16.800 align:middle line:90%
And that is our potential.

00:55:16.800 --> 00:55:19.860 align:middle line:84%
And to do that is
about remembering

00:55:19.860 --> 00:55:21.330 align:middle line:90%
the wholeness of all that is.

00:55:21.330 --> 00:55:23.340 align:middle line:90%
And we may not make it.

00:55:23.340 --> 00:55:25.750 align:middle line:90%
We may not make it.

00:55:25.750 --> 00:55:30.420 align:middle line:84%
But, for me, if we are to make
it, that is the process for us

00:55:30.420 --> 00:55:34.860 align:middle line:84%
collectively to come
together, to go through.

00:55:34.860 --> 00:55:39.660 align:middle line:84%
That is, for me, the next
step in the potential

00:55:39.660 --> 00:55:43.980 align:middle line:84%
of our conscious evolution and
literally our cosmic destiny.

00:55:43.980 --> 00:55:47.400 align:middle line:84%
This is, for me, what the
universe is calling to us,

00:55:47.400 --> 00:55:52.050 align:middle line:90%
is inviting us to be and to do.

00:55:52.050 --> 00:55:56.100 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, I want to make sure
that I give you the opportunity

00:55:56.100 --> 00:56:00.030 align:middle line:84%
